title: Iced Straw Guaw By Killer Fruits Vapetasia
description: One of the best options when it comes to vape juice is Killer Fruits Iced Straw Guaw by Vapetasia, which opens up a whole new flavor world. To ensure that your tastes are delighted with each puff, it combines a delicious strawberry flavor with an exotic guava flavor before finishing with a burst of cool menthol.
